<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4694266>
    dc:description "FIGURE 25. Male genitalia of Siberian Ennominae. A, B—Hypomecis roboraria; C, D—H. punctinalis; E, F—Ematurga atomaria; G, H—Deileptenia ribeata; I, J—Paradarisa consonaria; K, L—Alcis jubata. A, C, E, G, I, L—genital segment; B, D, F, H, J, K—phallos. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4694266/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4694316>
    dc:description "FIGURE 42. Female genitalia of Siberian Ennominae.A—Apoaspilates tristrigaria; B—Apocheima cinerarius; C—Hypomecis roboraria; D—H. punctinalis. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4694316/files/figure.png" ;
